descript.abstract: This shapefile is a simple point datafile of Idaho campgrounds. The intial dataset was obtained from the Idaho Department of Lands. Additional points were added from the Idaho Outdoor Recreation Facility Inventory and the 2008 RV Idaho Guide.
descript.purpose: To show public and private campgrounds throughout the State of idaho
descript.supplinf: The Idaho Department of Parks and Recreation plans to update this information with additional fields within the next year. This information should be used only for display purposes. The data has not been checked for accuracy.
